No information.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="D9F16554FFB7BA1BB1A7FC03B444F41A" pageId="11" pageNumber="630" type="activity">
<paragraph id="915436DFFFB7BA1BB1A7FC03B444F41A" blockId="11.[1459,2667,2086,3146]" pageId="11" pageNumber="630">
<emphasis id="A39FEACDFFB7BA1BB1A7FC03B482F44A" bold="true" box="[1461,1700,2915,2948]" pageId="11" pageNumber="630">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Chiribaya’s Bonneted Bat has been captured in mist nets set over blackwater rivers. Holotype was flying at c¢. 
<quantity id="56139B3AFFB7BA1BBC18FCEABA1CF465" box="[2058,2106,2954,2987]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.0" pageId="11" pageNumber="630" unit="m" value="5.0">5 m</quantity>
whenit struck the top of a gate and fell on the road.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="D9F16554FFB7BA1BB1A4FCB9BB44F434" box="[1462,2402,3033,3066]" pageId="11" pageNumber="630" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph id="915436DFFFB7BA1BB1A4FCB9BB44F434" blockId="11.[1459,2667,2086,3146]" box="[1462,2402,3033,3066]" pageId="11" pageNumber="630">
